<p>Kurron Ni is not on the truespirit faction but adjusts it.  The whole purpose of the first 3 things (kurron ni, cough medicine, tomb) is to raise your faction to the point that the others will talk to you.  Starting you low on the faction and needing to raise it with each step is the way verant tries to ensure you do the quest in a linear fashion. If you just start the quest and go through it normally you will have the faction you need for each NPC as you get to them.</p>
