<p>Good quest tricks.  But two things. <br /> <br />It doesn't have to be Capt Surestout.  Killing any of these 4 will spawn the lesser spirit for starting the shaman epic: <br />Capt Surestout (Ocean of Tears) <br />Blinde the Cutpurse (Rathe Mountains) <br />Peg Leg (Butcherblock Mountains) <br />an Iksar Manslayer (Field of Bone) <br /> <br />You don't have to make a macro with all 4 lines.  Just the final line to receive the gem:  /say I wish to know more <br /> <br /></p>
