<p>Not that hard to figure out...VI originally put it in so that you would not log in and already be taking a beating (because of lag, you can appear in the game before your computer is done) and if you had low health when you logged, you could theoretically be dead when you logged in, was a good idea but people just had to take advantage of it...</p>
