<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>The True Spirit Faction is needed to complete the Epic Quest for Shaman.  Your faction needs to be at a certain level in order to continue to the next part of the quest.  It is possible to increase your faction with the True Spirits by repeatedly completing the first part of the quest.</p>
